query:
SELECT 
  u.email,
  COUNT(qp.id) as progress_count,
  COUNT(DISTINCT qp.questionId) as unique_questions,
  SUM(CASE WHEN qp.firstAttemptStatus = 'incorrect' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as incorrect_count
FROM users u
LEFT JOIN question_progress qp ON u.id = qp.userId
WHERE u.email = 'testyou@me.com'
GROUP BY u.id, u.email;
